---
import SectionIconBadge from './SectionIconBadge.astro';
---

<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden border-t border-white/[0.05] px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20 md:px-10 md:py-24 lg:px-16"
  style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #080c14 0%, #0d1322 100%);"
>
  <!-- Background glow -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-48 left-1/2 h-[400px] w-[600px] -translate-x-1/2"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(30,64,175,0.15), transparent 70%);"
  ></div>

  <!-- Section Header -->
  <div class="relative mb-12 text-center sm:mb-16">
    <span
      class="inline-block bg-blue-muted/15 border border-blue-muted/30 text-blue-accent
             text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[3px] uppercase px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded mb-3"
      data-i18n="ai.label"
    >AI Integration</span>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-tight sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl">
      <span class="grad-text" data-i18n="ai.title1">AI 도구 연동,</span>
      <br />
      <span class="grad-text" data-i18n="ai.title2">자동으로 설정됩니다</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-lg text-sm text-text-muted sm:text-base" data-i18n="ai.sub">
      처음 실행하면 Claude Code, Codex, Gemini CLI 연동을 자동으로 설정합니다
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Cards Grid -->
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl grid-cols-1 gap-5 sm:gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

    <!-- Card 1: Zero-config (full width) -->
    <div
      class="card-top-line relative md:col-span-2 bg-white/[0.02] border border-blue-muted/15
             rounded-2xl p-5 sm:p-6 md:p-8"
    >
      <div class="mb-4">
        <SectionIconBadge name="bolt" />
      </div>
      <h3
        class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-2.5"
        data-i18n="ai.card1.title"
      >AI 연동 자동 설정</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4" data-i18n="ai.card1.desc">
        앱을 처음 실행하면 Claude Code, Codex, Gemini CLI 설정 파일을 찾아 필요한 훅을 등록합니다. 별도 설정 없이 바로 사용할 수 있습니다.
      </p>
      <!-- Tool chips -->
      <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {['Claude Code · settings.json', 'Codex · hooks.json', 'Gemini · settings.json'].map(t => (
          <span class="bg-blue-deep/20 border border-blue-muted/25 text-blue-accent/80 text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-md">{t}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
      <!-- Terminal demo -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-[#030712] p-4 font-mono text-xs">
        <div class="text-text-darkest" data-i18n="ai.card1.demoComment"># AI 도구 작업이 끝나면 CLIX가 자동으로 알림을 받습니다</div>
        <div class="text-text-primary mt-1">$ claude "리팩토링 마무리해줘"</div>
        <div class="text-text-darkest mt-1">... working ...</div>
        <div class="text-green-500 mt-1" data-i18n="ai.card1.demoSuccess">✓ Claude Code 작업 완료 → CLIX에 알림이 전달됨</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2: clix-notify -->
    <div
      class="card-top-line relative rounded-2xl border border-blue-muted/15 bg-white/[0.02] p-5 sm:p-6 md:p-8"
    >
      <div class="mb-4">
        <SectionIconBadge name="bell" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-2.5 whitespace-pre-line" data-i18n="ai.card2.title">clix-notify
인앱 알림</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4" data-i18n="ai.card2.desc">
        AI 작업이 끝나면 CLIX 안에서 바로 알림을 받을 수 있습니다. 오래 걸리는 작업을 계속 지켜보지 않아도 됩니다.
      </p>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-[#030712] p-4 font-mono text-xs">
        <div class="text-text-primary">$ clix-notify "배포 완료" --kind completed</div>
        <div class="text-blue-muted mt-1" data-i18n="ai.card2.demoOutput">→ CLIX 사이드바에 알림이 표시됨</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3: clix-handoff -->
    <div
      class="card-top-line relative rounded-2xl border border-blue-muted/15 bg-white/[0.02] p-5 sm:p-6 md:p-8"
    >
      <div class="mb-4">
        <SectionIconBadge name="route" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-2.5 whitespace-pre-line" data-i18n="ai.card3.title">clix-handoff
세션 핸드오프</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4" data-i18n="ai.card3.desc">
        다른 탭의 작업 디렉토리에서 AI 도구를 이어서 실행할 수 있습니다. 여러 서버를 오가며 작업할 때 유용합니다.
      </p>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-[#030712] p-4 font-mono text-xs">
        <div class="text-text-primary">$ clix-handoff tab-2 claude</div>
        <div class="text-blue-muted mt-1" data-i18n="ai.card3.demoOutput">→ tab-2 디렉토리에서 claude 실행</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
